OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEaster Sunday will start on a
OL,6,Frather cloudy, breezy and showery
OL,7,Fnote. The showers will become very
OL,8,Fisolated by the middle of the day
OL,9,Fthough, leaving plenty of sunny spells
OL,10,Ffor the afternoon. Feeling a bit
OL,11,Fcolder than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn isolated light shower is
OL,14,Fpossible early this evening, but with
OL,15,Fa ridge of high pressure toppling
OL,16,Facross overnight it looks largely dry
OL,17,Fwith clear periods. A slight frost
OL,18,Fforming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
