OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FEaster Monday should be a fine
OL,6,Fday. Some cloud is likely, especially
OL,7,Fduring the morning, and it will be
OL,8,Fbreezy. However, feeling a little
OL,9,Fwarmer when the sun breaks through.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday will be another dry day with
OL,13,Fsome warm sunshine, though breezy.
OL,14,FCloudier on Wednesday with some rain,
OL,15,Fthen brighter, but cooler and rather
OL,16,Fshowery on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
